sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as News Article Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database
    participant FS as Media Storage

    User->>UI: Open article by slug URL
    UI->>LW: Route model binding request
    LW->>DB: Resolve article by slug
    DB-->>LW: Article record
    LW->>FS: Resolve cover image URL
    FS-->>LW: Image URL
    LW-->>UI: Render title, date, content, image

    User->>UI: Back to list
    UI-->>UI: Navigate to news list page
